		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Now I'm curious; how different would the NES's video signal look if it output actual sine waves, instead of square waves?
<br />
<br />dwedit: Those colors look like they're just decoded using a lookup table or something. Is there something more to it than that?
<br />
<br />Edit: I just looked it up on Wikipedia, those are all NTSC artifacts? Pretty crazy!

		

